044package org.jfree.chart.renderer;
045
046/**
047 * An exception that is generated by the {@link Outlier}, {@link OutlierList}
048 * and {@link OutlierListCollection} classes.
049 */
050public class NotOutlierException extends Exception {
051
052    /**
053     * Creates a new exception.
054     *
055     * @param message  the exception message.
056     */
057    public NotOutlierException(String message) {
058        super(message);
059    }
060
061}
